dt-option.default:
        The default value for the `-init languages.searchPanes.title` paramater is `-type undefined`. When this is not in place the `-init i18n` function will use 'Filters Active - %d' as a default.


        As standard, SearchPanes will set the title to display the number of filters in the style of the following 'Filters Active - %d'.

        By overwriting this value in the initialisation, for whatever value, the relevant message will be shown. 

		This is useful for customising the title to fit best with the webpage it is being applied to. 





$(document).ready(function() {
    $('#example').DataTable( {
        searchPanes: true,
        language: {
            searchPanes: {
                title:{
                    _: 'Filters Selected - %d',
                    0: 'No Filters Selected',
                    1: 'One Filter Selected',
                }
            }
        }
    });
});
